  "Sanction Details" : "WITHOUT ADMITTING OR DENYING THE CHARGES BORGEN HAS AGREED TO BE SUSPENDED FROM ASSOCIATION WITH ANY INVESTMENT ADVISER FOR 180 DAYS. BORGEN AGREED TO CEASE AND DESIST FROM ANY SUCH VIOLATIONS, AND AGREED TO BE SUSPENDED FROM ASSOCIATION WITH ANY INVESTMENT ADVISER FOR 180 DAYS, PAY A $150,000 CIVIL MONETARY PENALTY, AND DISGORGE $590,000 TO CLIENTS WHOSE ACCOUNTS WERE ADVERSELY AFFECTED BY THE VIOLATIVE CONDUCT, WITH CREDIT BEING GIVEN FOR $85,000 WHICH THE FIRMPREVIOUSLY REMITTED TO SOME OF THOSE CLIENTS."
